# OBJECT::FORCE_PORTABLE_PICKUP_LAST_ACCESSIBLE_POSITION_SETTING

## Summary
Forces a portable pickup's last accessible position to be what its current position is in this frame

## Parameters
* **OBJECT_INDEX** pickupID
